Description_lang: Arrogance fills the player with Overconfidence increasing the amount of damage the player deals by $145891s2% as well as dealing $145891s1 Shadow damage to the player.  The player also gains stacks of Growing Overconfidence which increases the effect of Overconfidence by 10% per stack.  Standing next to an ally will cause them to gain Overconfidence, but reset your stacks of Growing Overconfidence to zero.
